summary: my old mod skimpy robe with glass and daedric variants
descriptionHtml:
--------------------Description--------------------------------
I returned my old mod. (mod is old and models and textures are not perfect)

Mod contains 2 variants: CBBE and UNP.
UNP:
Mod contains robe, necklace, gloves, boots.
Clothes variants of armor contains in chest in Whiterun near Dragonsreach - look screens.
Daedric and glass variants of robes, boots, gloves are craftable.

CBBE:
Mod contains robe redskirt, robe blackskirt, necklace, gloves, boots.
Leather, daedric and glass variants of robes, boots, gloves are craftable. (no clothes variant).

Also you can be interested in my other mod [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/82430]Ceremonial armor redone[/url]
